Package: ZoomCorrelation
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Zoom Visualization Based on Perfect Correlation Detection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Andres", "Mora", email = "andresmz1996@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An advanced visualization package that automatically triggers zoom 
    functionality when perfect correlation is detected between variables. 
    The package integrates statistical analysis with dynamic visualization, 
    providing enhanced data exploration capabilities for perfectly correlated 
    data points in ggplot2 plots.
